        },
        {
          "title": "Baraita on Borrowed Measuring Vessels: Vessel Ownership and Sub-Unit Pricing Determine When Possession Transfers",
          "display_title": "Vessel Ownership",
          "timestamp": "21:22"
        },
        {
          "title": "Gemara Refines the Case: When Prices Are Set for Sub-Units Like Logs per Sela, Each Unit Creates a Separate Completed Sale",
